{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"bg":"bg_adv_21143.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303501,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101901,"motion":1,"pos":2}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bgm":"bgm03_story07","chara":[{"id":101901}],"nameRight":"Tsukasa","textRight":"I see.","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":101901}],"textRight":"So that's why you left your house and were@hanging around here."},{"chara":[{"id":303501,"lipSynch":0}],"nameLeft":"Riko","textLeft":"..."},{"nameNarration":"Riko","narration":"The more I thought I had to help Mom @and Dad because they're so busy, @the worse I felt...","narrationBg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"narration":"It's not like I was thinking that@I wanted to be a good girl or anything."},{"narration":"I just wanted Mom and Dad@to know how lonely I was feeling."},{"chara":[{"id":101901,"motion":0}],"narrationEffect":"out","textRight":"I understand what's going on now."},{"chara":[{"id":101901}],"textRight":"Do you not have anyone else you can talk@to about this?"},{"chara":[{"id":101901}],"textRight":"Ah, right...you're an only child."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101901,"motion":100}],"textRight":"Oh, what about a friend then?"},{"chara":[{"id":303501,"lipSynch":0}],"textLeft":"..."},{"chara":[{"id":303501,"lipSynch":1}],"textLeft":"We...used to have this neighbor..."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":303501,"motion":100}],"textLeft":"She always looked after me ever since I was@little."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101901,"motion":1}],"textRight":"Oh, that's good. You should talk to her about@this!"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":303501,"motion":300}],"textLeft":"But...I can't."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101901}],"textRight":"What? Why?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":303501}],"textLeft":"She...got married, and moved far away."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":303501,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"I can't see her anymore. Plus I wouldn't want@to bother her..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":2,"id":303501,"tear":1}],"textLeft":"*Sniffle*"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":101901,"motion":400}],"textRight":"[chara:101901:effect_emotion_surprise_0][se:7226_shock]Ah! Don't cry!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101901,"motion":300}],"textRight":"Hey... Riko."},{"chara":[{"id":101901}],"textRight":"You got mad at your parents, right?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101901,"motion":200}],"textRight":"You told them they always made you lonely@and said, \"You're mean! I hate you!\""},{"bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":303501,"tear":0}],"textLeft":"I... I did."},{"bgm":"bgm03_story05","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101901,"motion":100}],"textRight":"Then why don't you tell your old neighbor@how sad you are? Be honest with her?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303501}],"textLeft":"I..."},{"chara":[{"id":101901,"motion":1}],"textRight":"She always looked after you, didn't she?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101901}],"textRight":"That means you're really important to her."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101901,"motion":0}],"textRight":"If you tell her how you feel..."},{"chara":[{"id":101901}],"textRight":"She, more than anyone else, [chara:101901:lipSynch_0][wait:1.0][chara:101901:cheek_0][chara:101901:face_mtn_ex_011.exp.json:motion_100][chara:101901:lipSynch_1]can accept @your loneliness head on."},{"chara":[{"id":303501,"lipSynch":0}],"textLeft":"..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":303501,"lipSynch":1}],"textLeft":"Tsukasa..."},{"chara":[{"id":101901,"motion":1}],"textRight":"*Giggle*"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101901}],"textRight":"Actually, I have a twin sister who doesn't@live with us."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"id":303501,"motion":100}],"textLeft":"What? You're a twin?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303501,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"Why don't you live together?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101901,"motion":300}],"textRight":"Ah... It's a long story."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101901,"motion":100}],"textRight":"But anyway, there's something we keep from@our parents."},{"chara":[{"id":101901}],"textRight":"Every so often, we meet up in secret."},{"chara":[{"id":101901,"motion":1}],"textRight":"Normally we live apart from each other, and@our lives couldn't be more different."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101901}],"textRight":"But when we meet up, we always have a lot @to talk about!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303501,"motion":400}],"textLeft":"A lot to talk about..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101901,"motion":0}],"textRight":"Where we live and what our lives are like can@be totally different..."},{"chara":[{"id":101901}],"textRight":"But it doesn't matter where you live, people@feel lonely or resentful all the same."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101901,"motion":100}],"textRight":"We can relate to each other about just about @anything when we talk. It's tons of fun!"},{"chara":[{"id":303501,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"...!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101901,"motion":1}],"textRight":"The same goes for you and your old neighbor."},{"chara":[{"id":101901}],"textRight":"You are in totally different places now,@but..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101901}],"textRight":"If you both want to see each other, there's@no reason why you can't."},{"chara":[{"id":303501,"lipSynch":0,"motion":200}],"textLeft":"...!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101901,"motion":0}],"textRight":"You're allowed to make a selfish request."},{"chara":[{"id":101901}],"textRight":"I mean, why not?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101901,"motion":100}],"textRight":"You're always such a good girl helping out@at the shop and all."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303501,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":303501,"lipSynch":1}],"textLeft":"Tsukasa... Thank you so much!"},{"chara":[{"id":101901,"motion":1}],"textRight":"Sure!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101901}],"textRight":"So, wanna go home now? I'll take you back."},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303501,"motion":200}],"textLeft":"Okay."},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"bg_adv_21083.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303501,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"id":303501,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Riko","textCenter":"...","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":0.4,"bg":"bg_adv_21143.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101901,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"blackFrame"},{"chara":[{"id":101901,"motion":100}],"nameCenter":"Tsukasa","textCenter":"Then why don't you tell your old neighbor how@sad you are? Be honest with her?","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":0.4,"bg":"bg_adv_21083.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303501,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"stop"},{"chara":[{"id":303501}],"nameCenter":"Riko","textCenter":"Mmm...","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":303501,"lipSynch":0}],"textCenter":"..."},{"nameNarration":"Narration","narration":"How about you?@Are you doing well in your new home?@You're not lonely?","narrationBg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","narrationEffect":"in","narrationHAlignment":"left","narrationPosX":180.0},{"narration":"I'm...really lonely without you.@Every day.@I remember when you were here,@and I feel really sad."},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":303501}],"narration":"I'm sorry for being so selfish.@But I really want to see you."},{"chara":[{"id":303501,"lipSynch":0}],"narrationEffect":"out","textCenter":"..."},{"chara":[{"id":303501,"lipSynch":0,"motion":300}],"textCenter":"(This request might make things hard for@her...)"},{"chara":[{"id":303501,"lipSynch":0}],"textCenter":"..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.4,"bg":"bg_adv_21143.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101901,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"blackFrame"},{"chara":[{"id":101901}],"nameCenter":"Tsukasa","textCenter":"If you tell her how you feel...","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":101901}],"textCenter":"She, more than anyone else, [chara:101901:lipSynch_0][wait:1.0][chara:101901:cheek_0][chara:101901:face_mtn_ex_011.exp.json:motion_100][chara:101901:lipSynch_1]can accept @your loneliness head on."},{"autoTurnLast":0.4,"bg":"bg_adv_21083.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":303501,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"stop"},{"chara":[{"id":303501,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Riko","textCenter":"...","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":303501,"lipSynch":1,"motion":400}],"textCenter":"No, no... I'm sure it'll be okay!"},{"chara":[{"id":303501,"motion":200}],"textCenter":"And...send!"},{"chara":[{"id":303501,"lipSynch":0}],"textCenter":"..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303501,"lipSynch":0}],"textCenter":"..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303501,"lipSynch":0,"motion":100}],"textCenter":"(I wonder when she'll reply?)"},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":800700,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":800600,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"id":800700}],"nameLeft":"Riko's Father","textLeft":"We're home.","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"nameRight":"Riko's Mother","textRight":"Riko, we're home. Sorry to get back so late."},{"chara":[{"id":800700,"lipSynch":0}],"textLeft":"Oh![chara:800700:cheek_0][chara:800700:face_mtn_ex_050.exp.json][chara:800700:lipSynch_1]"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":800700},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":800600}],"textLeft":"Shhh."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":800600}],"textRight":"She's asleep..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303501,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"turnChangeIn":"rollInFast"},{"chara":[{"id":303501,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Riko","textCenter":"...","turnChangeOut":"rollOutFast"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"bgm":"stop","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}